  "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Offer</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/899570/extras/afb00176d4f5b531396463aac091ef70.avif?t=1747502061\" width=650 height=212 /></span><br><br>My First Music Workshop is a unique music workshop simulator game where you need to fix musical instruments. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/899570/extras/b20079312501664f09603e924e874a3b.avif?t=1747502061\" width=650 height=212 /></span><br><br>Once you fix the instrument, you can collect your payment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/899570/extras/f77d9ea4cb40f45cf9bf628750c0001f.avif?t=1747502061\" width=650 height=212 /></span><br><br>Game Features:<br>* jobs related to repairing musical instruments<br>* jobs related to used gear that can be resold<br>* list of repairs that needs to be done to collect your payment<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/899570/extras/e9e6b31118f1d9129b20125b9747e9ea.avif?t=1747502061\" width=650 height=212 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/899570/extras/afb00176d4f5b531396463aac091ef70.avif?t=1747502061\" width=650 height=212 /></span><br><br>My First Music Workshop is a unique music workshop simulator game where you need to fix musical instruments. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/899570/extras/b20079312501664f09603e924e874a3b.avif?t=1747502061\" width=650 height=212 /></span><br><br>Once you fix the instrument, you can collect your payment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/899570/extras/f77d9ea4cb40f45cf9bf628750c0001f.avif?t=1747502061\" width=650 height=212 /></span><br><br>Game Features:<br>* jobs related to repairing musical instruments<br>* jobs related to used gear that can be resold<br>* list of repairs that needs to be done to collect your payment<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/899570/extras/e9e6b31118f1d9129b20125b9747e9ea.avif?t=1747502061\" width=650 height=212 /></span>",
